Residue from a number of spells is present in this punch; it looks like it was used as a delivery system for several different hexes, though no magical effects remain.  You can make out a miniaturization spell, a floral overgrowth curse, a brain-addler hex, and several more you can't identify.
> aurale Gwen

> aurale Gwen
A powerful temporal knot has been placed on her, freezing her in time.   She's essentially a statue, but on the plus side, the total stasis also makes her completely invulnerable.
