"AHHHH-CHOOO!"

Your photo from last year rubs her nose and looks up at you.

"Oh.  Hebbo.  Whad do you wadd?"

Quickly, you explain the situation.  She doesn't seem very interested.  "Thad's nod until neggst fall, ride?   I'b god all subber before I hab to worry aboud it.   I'b judge gonna relaggs and try to forget all aboud school."
