Fountain
This is the area in front of the school.   Saplings sprout from a poorly manicured lawn, and the elegant stained-glass windows are dull with dirt.   The path forks around a large fountain, meeting again on the other side and leading up to the front door to the east, or into the woods to the west.
You can go south, west or east.
You can see a partially-submerged garden gnome.
> use extractor on gnome

> use extractor on gnome
You securely attach the winch of the tooth extractor to the gnome's hat, back up several paces, brace against the side of the pool, and...

BRRRM!  The winch moans and grinds as it struggles against the ice.  You pull harder, feeling as if your arms are about to be ripped right out of their sockets.  Suddenly, you hear a crack, then another, and all of a sudden you fall backwards, landing on your rear end on the walk.  You watch the garden gnome shoot into the sky in a glittering burst of ice.   It hangs in the air for a second, them plummets down, nearly braining you, only to bounce off of the walk and land on the lawn.
> drop extractor

