Void
It is pitch black.   You are likely to be eaten by a squid.

The phenomenal pressure here means you're barely able to move, barely able to breathe.   You're numb with the intense cold.  You can see nothing.  You can hear nothing.  You can sense nothing.   There is nothing here but utter and total darkness.

You can go out.
