> aurale darkness

> aurale darkness
You detect a very powerful bundle of spellwork to your left and beneath you--in the complete absence of any other magic beyond your own, it shines like a beacon.   You crawl through the icy water until your tentacles encounter the craggy wall of the trench, then let yourself ooze downward towards the source of the signal.   Eventually you find it, half-buried in the muck at the very bottom of the trench.   Your feel along it with your fingers and tentacles, eventually working out the shape--a rough-hewn sarcophagus.   The magic is coming from inside.
> x sarcophagus

> x sarcophagus
