KA-THUDDDDDDDDDDDD!

SMASH!

CRUNCH!

You hear an enormous explosion from the direction of the Academy, followed by a series of crashes and tinkles.  It sounds like it's raining crockery somewhere.

Forest Path
You are on a stone path winding through thick forest.  To the west you can smell salt air and hear surf.  To the east, the path continues towards Whitefield Academy.  A faint trail leads north.
