Upper Rotunda
This is the second floor of the rotunda.   A broad walkway runs around the room; you can look over the ornately carved railings and see the ruins of the welcome party on the floor below.   The grand staircase leads down, the school library is to the north, and another exit lies to the south.
You can go down, north or south.
