"Take one heaping spoonful for relief of indigestion, nausea, and bloating caused by excessive food consumption.  Gluttonous Gus says: 'When I'm full, I chug it neat, and once against I'm Red-E-To-Eat!'  That's the DigestOl guarantee!"
