White-gold light envelopes the trophy, and in one smooth stroke, the little metal bowler completes his throw, loosing the ball-bearing-sized bowling ball to fly through the air.  It bounces against the juice boxes, unbalancing them, and drops to the floor before rolling off into the corner.   Several juice boxes tumble from the shelf, landing on the lower shelf or the floor, though you still can't reach any of them.  One carton of orange punch falls behind the canister of DigestOl, nearly pushing it off of the shelf.
